Lianyungang Municipal Party Committee Secretary Jianhua Wang Meets International Chamber of Commerce Mission.\n\n

  	&nbsp;

  		&nbsp;

  		Recently,&nbsp;Lianyungang&nbsp;Municipal&nbsp;Committee,&nbsp;Municipal&nbsp;People&#39;s&nbsp;Congress&nbsp;Chairman&nbsp;Jianhua&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;met&nbsp;with&nbsp;CUSCC&nbsp;president&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Wynn&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;party.&nbsp;Vice&nbsp;Mayor&nbsp;Shi&nbsp;Yan&nbsp;and&nbsp;director&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Overseas&nbsp;Chinese&nbsp;Affairs&nbsp;Juan&nbsp;Liu&nbsp;attended&nbsp;the&nbsp;meeting.
  		
  		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;reported&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;United&nbsp;States&nbsp;and&nbsp;International&nbsp;Business&nbsp;Delegation&nbsp;members&nbsp;are&nbsp;mostly&nbsp;financial,&nbsp;business&nbsp;executives&nbsp;and&nbsp;community&nbsp;leaders&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;certain&nbsp;investment&nbsp;intentions.&nbsp;This&nbsp;is&nbsp;mainly&nbsp;to&nbsp;connect&nbsp;with&nbsp;&quot;Jiang&nbsp;Su&nbsp;Dongrong&nbsp;eco-industrial&nbsp;base&quot;&nbsp;and&nbsp;&quot;Jiang&nbsp;Su&nbsp;Dongrong&nbsp;end&nbsp;parties&nbsp;Paradise&quot;&nbsp;two&nbsp;projects&nbsp;in&nbsp;city&nbsp;Guanyun.
  		
  		&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;During&nbsp;the&nbsp;meeting,&nbsp;Jianhua&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;had&nbsp;a&nbsp;warm&nbsp;welcome&nbsp;to&nbsp;Wynn&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;and&nbsp;his&nbsp;collegues,&nbsp;and&nbsp;introduced&nbsp;Lianyungang&nbsp;situation&nbsp;to&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Wynn&nbsp;Wang.&nbsp;He&nbsp;said&nbsp;Lianyungang&nbsp;is&nbsp;located&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;central&nbsp;eastern&nbsp;coast&nbsp;of&nbsp;China,&nbsp;is&nbsp;China&#39;s&nbsp;key&nbsp;harbor&nbsp;city.&nbsp;To&nbsp;the&nbsp;south,&nbsp;it&nbsp;connected&nbsp;to&nbsp;Delta&nbsp;economic&nbsp;circle&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Yangtze;&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;north,&nbsp;Japan,&nbsp;South&nbsp;Korea&nbsp;&nbsp;are&nbsp;across&nbsp;the&nbsp;sea,&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;west&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;known&nbsp;as&nbsp;the&nbsp;&quot;New&nbsp;Silk&nbsp;Road&quot;&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;Eurasian&nbsp;continental&nbsp;bridge&nbsp;to&nbsp;Europe.&nbsp;Jianhua&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;Said,&nbsp;Lianyungang&rsquo;s&nbsp;location,&nbsp;has&nbsp;obvious&nbsp;advantages&nbsp;of&nbsp;transportation&nbsp;and&nbsp;resources.&nbsp;With&nbsp;favorable&nbsp;conditions&nbsp;for&nbsp;potential&nbsp;investment&nbsp;and&nbsp;development,&nbsp;it&nbsp;is&nbsp;increasingly&nbsp;being&nbsp;favored&nbsp;by&nbsp;investors&nbsp;at&nbsp;home&nbsp;and&nbsp;abroad.&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;Wynn&nbsp;said&nbsp;Lianyungang&nbsp;&nbsp;has&nbsp;superior&nbsp;investment&nbsp;environment,&nbsp;hoping&nbsp;to&nbsp;have&nbsp;deeper&nbsp;understanding&nbsp;of&nbsp;Lianyungang&nbsp;for&nbsp;seeking&nbsp;greater&nbsp;space&nbsp;of&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;Chamber&nbsp;of&nbsp;Commerce.
